We are 𝑠𝑡𝑖𝑟-𝑓𝑟𝑦𝑖𝑛’ up some rewards for a couple of lucky Vikings! Our delicious dish has one item that doesn’t belong, can you tell us which one it is?! 😋Let us know for a chance to win!🤩
